memberdef.name: YY_INPUT
memberdef.initializer: if ( YY_CURRENT_BUFFER_LVALUE->yy_is_interactive ) \ { \ int c = '*'; \ yy_size_t n; \ for ( n = 0; n < max_size && \ (c = getc( psfwin )) != EOF && c != '\n'; ++n ) \ buf[n] = (char) c; \ if ( c == '\n' ) \ buf[n++] = (char) c; \ if ( c == EOF && ferror( psfwin ) ) \ YY_FATAL_ERROR( "input in flex scanner failed" ); \ result = n; \ } \ else \ { \ errno=0; \ while ( (result = fread(buf, 1, max_size, psfwin))==0 && ferror(psfwin)) \ { \ if( errno != EINTR) \ { \ YY_FATAL_ERROR( "input in flex scanner failed" ); \ break; \ } \ errno=0; \ clearerr(psfwin); \ } \ }\ \
